n_features_to_remove_list = [4, 5, 6, 8, 11, 14]

best_params_roc_log = None


results = []

warnings.filterwarnings(action="ignore")

for n_features_to_remove in tqdm(n_features_to_remove_list):
    features_to_remove = feature_weights.nsmallest(
        n_features_to_remove, "absolute_weight"
    )["feature"].values
    features_train_reduced = features_train_code.drop(columns=features_to_remove)

    model = LogisticRegression(
        random_state=RANDOM_STATE, max_iter=1000
    )
    grid_search = GridSearchCV(model, param_grid=param_grid, cv=cv, scoring="roc_auc", n_jobs=-1)
    grid_search.fit(features_train_reduced, target_train)

    #   
    best_params = grid_search.best_params_
   
    #     
    best_model = model.set_params(**best_params)

    best_model.fit(features_train_reduced, target_train)
    best_score = grid_search.best_score_

    #  accuracy
    accuracy = best_model.score(features_train_reduced, target_train)

    results.append(
        {
            "n_features_to_remove": n_features_to_remove,
            "ROC-AUC": grid_search.best_score_,
            "Accuracy": accuracy,
            "Best params": grid_search.best_params_,
        })
        
    if  best_model_roc_log is None or grid_search.best_score_ > best_model_roc_log.best_score_:
        best_model_roc_log = grid_search
        best_params_roc_log = best_params
        
    

results_df = pd.DataFrame(results)

n_features_to_remove_list = [5, 6, 7]

results = []

best_model_roc_gbm = None
best_params_roc_gbm = None

for n_features_to_remove in tqdm(n_features_to_remove_list):
    features_to_remove = importan.nsmallest(n_features_to_remove, "importance")[
        "feature"
    ].values
    features_train_reduced = features_train_code.drop(columns=features_to_remove)

    #   
    param_grid = {
        "learning_rate": [0.01, 0.05, 0.1, 0.2],
        "max_depth": [2, 3, 5, 7],
        "n_estimators": [50, 100, 200, 1000],
        "num_leaves": [2, 3, 4, 5],
    }

    model = lgb.LGBMClassifier(
        class_weight="balanced",
        random_state=RANDOM_STATE,
        verbosity=0,
        force_col_wise=True,
    )

    cv = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=5, shuffle=True, random_state=RANDOM_STATE)

    grid_search = GridSearchCV(model, param_grid, cv=cv, scoring="roc_auc", n_jobs=-1)

    #     GridSearchCV
    grid_search.fit(features_train_reduced, target_train)
    #   
    best_params = grid_search.best_params_
    #     
    best_model = model.set_params(**best_params)
    best_model.fit(features_train_reduced, target_train)

    #  accuracy
    accuracy = best_model.score(features_train_reduced, target_train)

    results.append(
        {
            "n_features_to_remove": n_features_to_remove,
            "ROC-AUC": grid_search.best_score_,
            "Accuracy": accuracy,
            "Best params": grid_search.best_params_,
        }
    )

    if best_model_roc_gbm is None or grid_search.best_score_ > best_model_roc_gbm.best_score_:
        best_model_roc_gbm = grid_search
        best_params_roc_gbm = best_params

    model = RandomForestClassifier(class_weight='balanced', random_state=RANDOM_STATE)

    cv = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=5, shuffle=True, random_state=RANDOM_STATE)

    grid_search = GridSearchCV(model, param_grid, cv=cv, scoring="roc_auc", n_jobs=-1)

    #     GridSearchCV
    grid_search.fit(features_train_reduced, target_train)     
    #   
    best_params = grid_search.best_params_
    #     
    best_model = model.set_params(**best_params)
    best_model.fit(features_train_reduced, target_train)

    #  accuracy
    accuracy = best_model.score(features_train_reduced, target_train)
    
    results.append({'n_features_to_remove': n_features_to_remove,
                    'ROC-AUC': grid_search.best_score_,
                    'Accuracy': accuracy,
                    'Best params': grid_search.best_params_})
    
    if best_model_roc_rf is None or grid_search.best_score_ > best_model_roc_rf.best_score_:
        best_model_roc_rf = grid_search
        best_params_roc_rf = best_params
    
results_df = pd.DataFrame(results)

print('Best model ROC-AUC:', best_model_roc_rf.best_score_)
print('Best model params:', best_params_roc_rf)
